      "message": "Line 342: 🟡 Suggestion: Mixed clipboard URL payloads can still drop non-local URLs. If the clipboard contains both local files and a web URL, this emits files but never pastes the web URL text because `pastedLocalFile` suppresses `newTextPasted()`. Consider explicitly pasting text whenever any non-local URL is present.\n```suggestion\n        bool pastedLocalFile \u003d false;\n        bool hasNonLocalUrl \u003d false;\n        for (const QUrl\u0026 url : urlList) {\n            if (url.isLocalFile()) {\n                Q_EMIT newFilePasted(url.toLocalFile());\n                pastedLocalFile \u003d true;\n            } else {\n                hasNonLocalUrl \u003d true;\n            }\n        }\n        if (!pastedLocalFile || hasNonLocalUrl)\n            Q_EMIT newTextPasted();\n```",
